id=\"84043443-14f2-4e6a-8179-b7ac2b2686ba\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 372.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 108.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 279.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Portal / Servicio</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>Dise&ntilde;o de pantallas + experiencia UX/UI (esto corre por cuenta de Qubika)</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">40</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Setup del proyecto nuevo con todas las herramientas (rubocop, sentry, simplecov, github actions)</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">32</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Vista de ingreso de correo</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Endpoint para inicio de reseteo de contrase&ntilde;a</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar el endpoint de inicio de reseteo de contrase&ntilde;a para que no env&iacute;e el OTP y refactorear el correo.</p><p>Ademas verificar y si el reset_token no est&aacute; expirado, enviar el mismo.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td><td><p>[auth-service]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Vista de success en el envio de correo con boton para reenviar el correo</p><p /><p><em>Para el reenv&iacute;o de correo, llamar el endpoint de reinicio de contrase&ntilde;a</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear vista para el ingreso de nueva contrase&ntilde;a.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em>En el caso de requerir OTP, pegarle a un endpoint para enviar el mismo, mostrar el input para ingresarlo y bot&oacute;n para reenviarlo</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">32</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Endpoint para el env&iacute;o de OTP</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Endpoint para generaci&oacute;n y env&iacute;o de OTP para reseteo de contrase&ntilde;a. Modificar texto de SMS</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td><td><p>[auth-service]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Endpoint para recepci&oacute;n de nuevas contrase&ntilde;as y c&oacute;digo OTP en el caso que aplique</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Revisar y refactorear endpoint de reseteo de contrase&ntilde;a</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>[auth-service]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Vista de success en el reseteo de contrase&ntilde;a con bot&oacute;n de redirect a la return_url</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>[auth-portal-new]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar el portal nuevo</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>[bancard-docker]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar configuraci&oacute;n del portal nuevo</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>[bancard-configurations]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Configuraci&oacute;n de m&aacute;quina de auth-portal en staging</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">2</p></td><td><p>[infrastructura]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Configuraci&oacute;n de proxy dmz para auth-portal en staging</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">2</p></td><td><p>[infrastructura]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Configuraci&oacute;n de maquinas de auth-portal en producci&oacute;n</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>[infrastructura]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Configuraci&oacute;n de proxy dmz para auth-portal en producci&oacute;n</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>[infrastructura]</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Refactor del endpoint request_reset en auth-service</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em>Agregar columna requires_otp en la tabla services y modificar operaci&oacute;n validate_otp? para que en lugar de recibir el requires_otp por par&aacute;metro lo consulte desde la tabla servicios por el servicio asociado al usuario.</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>[auth-service]</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#f4f5f7\"><p>Gestion 15% (no altera el scope, es por tema de facturaci&oacute;n)</p></td><td><p>35</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#f4f5f7\"><p>Dise&ntilde;o + Experiencia UX/UI (esto va por cuenta de Qubika)</p></td><td><p>40</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#f4f5f7\"><p>Total desarrollo</p></td><td><p>232</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>Total hs desarrollo + gesti&oacute;n - Sin dise&ntilde;o</p></td><td><p>267</p></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3022290990"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":693},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3022290990/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3022290990/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3022290990/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3022290990/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3022290990","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3022290990/Nuevo+Portal+de+Reseteo+de+Contrase+a+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3022290990","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3022290990","tinyui":"/x/LoAkt","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https:/